<th id="9E09727F1F71004FFFE9FE43FE8832B1" box="[115,290,418,438]" gridcol="0" gridrow="5" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">Pétales</th>
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFEA0FE43FD0D32B1" box="[314,679,418,438]" gridcol="1" gridrow="5" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">soudés jusqu’à mi-longueur;</td>
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFD5AFE43FB0F32B1" box="[704,1189,418,438]" gridcol="2" gridrow="5" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">soudés jusqu’à 1/3 de leur longueur;</td>
</tr>
<tr id="DDD81B031F71004FFFE9FE5DFB0F32D7" box="[115,1189,444,464]" gridrow="6" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">
<th id="9E09727F1F71004FFFE9FE5DFE8832D7" box="[115,290,444,464]" gridcol="0" gridrow="6" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">Sépales et pétales</th>
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFEA0FE5DFD0D32D7" box="[314,679,444,464]" gridcol="1" gridrow="6" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">non ponctués;</td>
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFD5AFE5DFB0F32D7" box="[704,1189,444,464]" gridcol="2" gridrow="6" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">lâchement ponctués;</td>
</tr>
<tr id="DDD81B031F71004FFFE9FE36FB0F32EC" box="[115,1189,471,491]" gridrow="7" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">
<th id="9E09727F1F71004FFFE9FE36FE8832EC" box="[115,290,471,491]" gridcol="0" gridrow="7" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">Étamines</th>
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFEA0FE36FD0D32EC" box="[314,679,471,491]" gridcol="1" gridrow="7" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">nettement plus courtes que les pétales,</td>
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFD5AFE36FB0F32EC" box="[704,1189,471,491]" gridcol="2" gridrow="7" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">presque aussi longues que les pétales, s’insérant</td>
</tr>
<tr id="DDD81B031F71004FFFE9FE0EFB0F3104" box="[115,1189,495,515]" gridrow="8" pageId="58" pageNumber="337" rowspan-0="1">
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFEA0FE0EFD0D3104" box="[314,679,495,515]" gridcol="1" gridrow="8" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">s’insérant sur le tube de la corolle un</td>
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFD5AFE0EFB0F3104" box="[704,1189,495,515]" gridcol="2" gridrow="8" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">sur le tube au niveau des lobes;</td>
</tr>
<tr id="DDD81B031F71004FFFE9FDE6FB0F311C" box="[115,1189,519,539]" gridrow="9" pageId="58" pageNumber="337" rowspan-0="1" rowspan-2="1">
<td id="9E09727F1F71004FFEA0FDE6FD0D311C" box="[314,679,519,539]" gridcol="1" gridrow="9" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">peu en-dessous des lobes;</td>
</tr>
</table>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="635719411F71FF8AFF12FD32FDB7304B" blockId="58.[111,648,596,844]" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">
Cette variété 
<emphasis id="519CC5531F71FF8AFE82FD32FE1031EA" box="[280,442,723,749]" italics="true" pageId="58" pageNumber="337">longipetiolatum</emphasis>
var. nov., de statut assez incertain, paraissant rare, tout en croissant dans des zones aujourd’hui faiblement menacées, peut être considérée comme vulnérable.
</paragraph>
